title: (Mon Full) Our Weekend at our iHeartCountry Festival and Which Artist ‘Won’ The Entire Thing + Lunchbox Interviews Guy Fieri…And It’s Painful + Actors Who Tried Music Game
itunes:title: (Mon Full) Our Weekend at our iHeartCountry Festival and Which Artist ‘Won’ The Entire Thing + Lunchbox Interviews Guy Fieri…And It’s Painful + Actors Who Tried Music Game
description:
We spent the weekend at our iHeartCountry Festival and shared our stories and favorite moments.  Lunchbox gets an exclusive interview with Guy Fieri…but the circumstances around it were not the best. Can the show guess the famous actor based on their music? Listen and find out!
